{"tid":695721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬為新帥列出5大條件","createTime":"2018-06-09T12:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T02:31:17.000Z","uid":31314,"like":159,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"cee8d89caa58812505ab3046b0b1a93eb6c6ed08","tid":695721,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里正找尋施丹接班人，據知新任主帥除了要有一定程度的執教功力，言行舉止亦非常重要。 <br />\n<br />\n根據西班牙《阿斯報》爆料，皇家馬德里在施丹（Zinedine Zidane）辭任教練一職後，已就新主帥列出5大條件。<br />\n<br />\n1：此人一定要懂多國語言<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Wenger knows six different languages - French, German, English, Spanish, Italian and some Japanese. </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2：而且有優雅外型，於場邊像施丹一樣，不時以整齊的西裝示人；不懂說西班牙語及喜歡穿運動裝的利物浦主帥高普，似乎不合格。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTHR1iHUcAAtvDl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCTHR1iHUcAAtvDl.jpg&h=f86d7c9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://i3.irishmirror.ie/incoming/article6784391.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/ONE-USE-ONLY-Arsene-Wenger.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.irishmirror.ie%2Fincoming%2Farticle6784391.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615b%2FONE-USE-ONLY-Arsene-Wenger.jpg&h=2d1b504d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3：新帥不能夠屬於舊派，必須要以新思維領軍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Wenger&rsquo;s first revolutionary shift occurred on the training field. He earned his nickname &ldquo;The Professor&rdquo; thanks to his precise planning and meticulous preparation.<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n4：更要跟球員打成一片，在更衣室受一眾球員尊重。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.vavel.com/b/101%20great%20goals%20th14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.vavel.com%2Fb%2F101%2520great%2520goals%2520th14.jpg&h=39e59a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5：最後，此人要注重球員的體能<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/67/590x/secondary/spt-ai-arsenal-traini-2-5-213140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F67%2F590x%2Fsecondary%2Fspt-ai-arsenal-traini-2-5-213140.jpg&h=6908980c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事關皇馬一向在下半場發力，所以保持球員整季都有十足狀態，是十分重要的事。 另外，意大利傳媒廣泛報道，皇馬新帥候選人之一的車路士領隊干地，雖很大機會在今夏離隊，但有傳已拒絕了皇馬的邀請。"},{"pid":"c351b82861ceca3960f880a14f63d538a59871b1","tid":695721,"uid":59678,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:21:43.000Z","msg":"爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7a7b2b9e1e8d393df7b1667f66be85f9373619","tid":695721,"uid":36497,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743d7883099bbf94ab5231979ce66d08e7e99a93","tid":695721,"uid":46835,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"我真係好想睇皇馬點培育幼齒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33763e05e6f1101abb6811367ac32f60a18cb0d1","tid":695721,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd7a7b2b9e1e8d393df7b1667f66be85f9373619","tid":695721,"uid":36497,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"豬蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33333eb382a622a20265847cb16b21899b332ea3","tid":695721,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"三連歐冠都要走<br />\n爺爺玩到幾耐"},{"pid":"e18c8c495081f2a638fbb2a1bf47d8781a0013b2","tid":695721,"uid":188867,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"先破紀錄價買入